ule before coming so you can watch it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SlZESjFZVEpIUkY5Q1lpMWpaRTk1VjJsVGRXYxAB!2m1!1s0x357ca2c74aeddea1:0x8b3046532cc715f6", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SlZESjFZVEpIUkY5Q1lpMWpaRTk1VjJsVGRXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "authorAttribution": {"uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106061387136457950815/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEa8f5c8eL6dQdudClvZnTERgpOsGOVTyEpYAbc0RGTPPGWYym=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7", "displayName": "Rex Tan"}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJod7tSseifDUR9hXHLFNGMIs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSUVUwcE1NbXgwVlc5VVMyWXpORE50Y3pnemFYYxAB", "text": {"text": "Must visit if you are in the area. You can walk around and explore and there are options to rent traditional clothing for the perfect photo ops. You can watch the Changing of the Royal Guard Ceremony, held at 10:00 AM and 2:00 PM, and this is outside of the admission area so you do not even need a ticket to see this. A bit touristy and the art is not very intricate but it is quite lovely. The Palace grounds are well-maintained and the buildings showcase traditional structures but you cannot explore deeper than an external view.", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 5, "publishTime": "2025-12-13T02:21:41.403572965Z", "originalText": {"text": "Must visit if you are in the area. You can walk around and explore and there are options to rent traditional clothing for the perfect photo ops. You can watch the Changing of the Royal Guard Ceremony, held at 10:00 AM and 2:00 PM, and this is outside of the admission area so you do not even need a ticket to see this. A bit touristy and the art is not very intricate but it is quite lovely. The Palace grounds are well-maintained and the buildings showcase traditional structures